{
  "info": {
    "name": "ETA Eats v2",
    "description": "Complete API collection for ETA Eats v2 — highway food pre-ordering platform.\n\n**Variables** (edit in the collection Variables tab):\n- `base_url` — e.g. http://localhost:8000\n- `access_token` — auto-filled by the OTP Verify request\n- `refresh_token` — auto-filled by the OTP Verify request\n- `phone_number` — your seed passenger phone e.g. +919000000001\n- `otp_code` — check server console logs in dev\n- `bus_id`, `qr_token`, `restaurant_id`, `menu_item_id`\n- `menu_category_id`, `cart_id`, `cart_item_id`, `order_id`\n- `operator_id`, `route_id`, `assignment_id`, `notification_id`\n- `razorpay_order_id`, `razorpay_payment_id`, `razorpay_signature`\n\n**Quick start**:\n1. Set `base_url` and `phone_number`\n2. Run **Request OTP** — OTP prints to server console\n3. Run **Verify OTP** — `access_token` and `refresh_token` are captured automatically\n4. All other requests use `{{access_token}}` in Authorization header",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "base_url",            "value": "http://localhost:8000",  "type": "string" },
    { "key": "access_token",        "value": "",                        "type": "string" },
    { "key": "refresh_token",       "value": "",                        "type": "string" },
    { "key": "phone_number",        "value": "+919000000001",           "type": "string" },
    { "key": "otp_code",            "value": "",                        "type": "string" },
    { "key": "bus_id",              "value": "1",                       "type": "string" },
    { "key": "qr_token",            "value": "",                        "type": "string" },
    { "key": "restaurant_id",       "value": "1",                       "type": "string" },
    { "key": "menu_category_id",    "value": "1",                       "type": "string" },
    { "key": "menu_item_id",        "value": "1",                       "type": "string" },
    { "key": "cart_id",             "value": "",                        "type": "string" },
    { "key": "cart_item_id",        "value": "1",                       "type": "string" },
    { "key": "order_id",            "value": "",                        "type": "string" },
    { "key": "operator_id",         "value": "1",                       "type": "string" },
    { "key": "route_id",            "value": "1",                       "type": "string" },
    { "key": "assignment_id",       "value": "1",                       "type": "string" },
    { "key": "notification_id",     "value": "1",                       "type": "string" },
    { "key": "razorpay_order_id",   "value": "",                        "type": "string" },
    { "key": "razorpay_payment_id", "value": "",                        "type": "string" },
    { "key": "razorpay_signature",  "value": "",                        "type": "string" }
  ],
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{access_token}}", "type": "string" }]
  },
  "item": [

    {
      "name": "🔐 Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Request OTP",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/otp/request/", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","v1","auth","otp","request",""] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } },
              "raw": "{\n  \"phone_number\": \"{{phone_number}}\"\n}"
            },
            "description": "Public. Sends an OTP to the given phone number. In dev the OTP is printed to the server console."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Verify OTP  [auto-captures tokens]",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.tokens) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('access_token',  json.tokens.access);",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('refresh_token', json.tokens.refresh);",
                  "    console.log('Tokens captured.');",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/otp/verify/", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","v1","auth","otp","verify",""] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } },
              "raw": "{\n  \"phone_number\": \"{{phone_number}}\",\n  \"code\": \"{{otp_code}}\"\n}"
            },
            "description": "Verifies the OTP. On success returns `{user, tokens}`. The test script automatically saves `access_token` and `refresh_token` to collection variables."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Refresh Access Token",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.access) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('access_token', json.access);",
                  "    console.log('access_token refreshed.');",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/token/refresh/", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","v1","auth","token","refresh",""] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } },
              "raw": "{\n  \"refresh\": \"{{refresh_token}}\"\n}"
            },
            "description": "Exchange a refresh token for a new access token. Test script auto-updates `access_token`."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Logout",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/logout/", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","v1","auth","logout",""] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } },
              "raw": "{\n  \"refresh\": \"{{refresh_token}}\"\n}"
            },
            "description": "Blacklists the refresh token. Returns 204. Client should discard both tokens."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get My Profile",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/me/", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","v1","auth","me",""] },
            "description": "Returns the currently authenticated user's profile."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Update My Profile",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/me/", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","v1","auth","me",""] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } },
              "raw": "{\n  \"full_name\": \"Arjun Sharma\",\n  \"email\": \"arjun@example.com\",\n  \"gender\": \"M\"\n}"
            },
            "description": "Partial update — only send fields you want to change."
          }
        }
      ]
    },

